title: Alexandra Kiroi-Bogatyreva
summary: Alexandra Kiroi-Bogatyreva (born 4 March 2002) is an Australian rhythmic gymnast. Kiroi-Bogatyeva was the 2018, 2019 and 2022 Australian All Around Rhythmic Gymnastics Champion. She won gold medal at 2022 Commonwealth Games for her clubs routine in individual apparatus finals.
